# Bracket Manager PRO - Quick Start

**Get trading in 5 minutes!** | Professional Version

---

## What is PRO?

PRO is the **professional version** with:
- âœ… Multiple Risk:Reward ratios (1:1, 1:2, 1:3, 2:1, 3:1, Custom)
- âœ… Drag-and-drop interface with real-time overlay
- âœ… Hotkeys (Ctrl+Shift+B toggle, Ctrl+Shift+R cycle ratios)
- âœ… Position scaling (multiple bracket sets)
- âœ… Breakeven buttons (2 configurable)
- âœ… Configurable trailing stop
- âœ… Sound alerts
- âœ… Full settings window
- âœ… User-based license (Vendor ID: 492)

**Want simpler?** LITE version offers fixed 1:2 ratio with no configuration needed!

