## Real-Time Overlay (PRO Feature)

As you drag, you'll see an overlay showing:
```
R:R: 1:2
Entry: 4500.00
â†’ SL: 4490.00 (-10.00)
  TP: 4520.00 (+20.00)
```

- **â†’** arrow shows which level you're currently setting
- **Position**: Top Right, Top Left, or Follow Mouse (configurable in settings)
- **Toggle**: Enable/disable in Settings â†’ Display tab

---

## Hotkeys (PRO Feature)

| Action | Hotkey | Description |
|--------|--------|-------------|
| Toggle tool on/off | **Ctrl+Shift+B** | Enable/disable bracket tool |
| Cycle R:R ratios | **Ctrl+Shift+R** | Switch between ratios |

**Cycle Order**: 1:1 â†’ 1:2 â†’ 1:3 â†’ 2:1 â†’ 3:1 â†’ Custom â†’ (repeat)

When you cycle ratios, you'll see:
- Toast notification showing new ratio
- Button updates to show current ratio
- Sound alert (if enabled)

---

## Example: Long at ES 4500

You're **long ES at 4500** and want to set brackets with 1:2 ratio:

**Method 1 - Drag to set Stop Loss**:
- Press **Ctrl+Shift+B** (button turns green)
- Drag DOWN to 4490
- Overlay shows: R:R 1:2, SL 4490, TP 4520
- Release
- âœ“ Result: SL @ 4490, TP @ 4520 (10 risk, 20 reward)

**Method 2 - Drag to set Take Profit**:
- Press **Ctrl+Shift+B** (button turns green)
- Drag UP to 4520
- Overlay shows: R:R 1:2, SL 4490, TP 4520
- Release
- âœ“ Result: SL @ 4490, TP @ 4520 (10 risk, 20 reward)

**Both methods work!** The overlay confirms prices before you release.

---

## Risk:Reward Ratios

PRO offers 6 preset ratios plus custom:

| Ratio | Meaning | Example | Best For |
|-------|---------|---------|----------|
| **1:1** | Equal risk/reward | Risk \$10, Make \$10 | Conservative, breakeven exits, scalping |
| **1:2** | Risk 1 to make 2 | Risk \$10, Make \$20 | **Most popular**, balanced approach |
| **1:3** | Risk 1 to make 3 | Risk \$10, Make \$30 | Aggressive, let winners run |
| **2:1** | Risk 2 to make 1 | Risk \$20, Make \$10 | Scalping with wider stops |
| **3:1** | Risk 3 to make 1 | Risk \$30, Make \$10 | Quick scalps, high win rate strategies |
| **Custom** | Your choice | Risk 1, Make 2.5 | Specific strategies requiring exact ratios |

**Switch ratios instantly**: Press **Ctrl+Shift+R** to cycle through all ratios!

**Recommended starting point**: **1:2 ratio**

---

## Position Scaling (Advanced)

Want to scale out of positions with **one drag**? Enable **Multiple Bracket Sets**:

### How It Works
1. Click **âš™** â†’ **Bracket Sets** tab
2. Check **"Enable Multiple Bracket Sets"**
3. Configure your splits:
   ```
   50% @ 1:1 ratio  â† Lock in early profit
   30% @ 1:2 ratio  â† Main target
   20% @ 1:3 ratio  â† Let it run
   ```
4. Click **Save**

Now when you drag, **one motion creates all three bracket sets** automatically!

### Example
- Long 10 contracts ES @ 4500
- Drag to set risk at 10 points
- Tool places:
  - 5 contracts: SL @ 4490, TP @ 4510 (1:1)
  - 3 contracts: SL @ 4490, TP @ 4520 (1:2)
  - 2 contracts: SL @ 4490, TP @ 4530 (1:3)

**Important**: All sets share the SAME Stop Loss for full position protection.

**Benefits**:
- Lock in profits early while letting some run
- Reduce stress by securing gains
- Professional money management

---

## Settings Window (âš™ Button)

Click the **âš™** gear button to access full configuration:

### Risk/Reward Tab
- Select default R:R ratio (1:1, 1:2, 1:3, 2:1, 3:1, Custom)
- Configure custom ratio values
- Current setting shows on main button

### Bracket Sets Tab
- Enable/disable position scaling
- Configure percentage splits for each bracket set
- Assign R:R ratio to each set
- Preview allocation before trading

### Display Tab
- Toggle drag overlay on/off
- Choose overlay position (Top Right, Top Left, Follow Mouse)
- Adjust visual preferences

### Position Management Tab (NEW)
- **Breakeven Buttons**:
  - Enable/disable each button (Button 1 and Button 2)
  - Configure tick offsets (e.g., BE+1, BE+5, or any custom value)
  - Set visibility preferences
- **Trailing Stop**:
  - Enable/disable trailing stop feature
  - Configure trailing tick amount (5, 10, 15, 20, or custom)
  - Adjust update frequency

### Audio Tab
- Enable/disable sound alerts
- Adjust volume
- Sounds for: success, error, cycle ratio

### Advanced Tab
- Enable debug logging (troubleshooting only)
- View log file location
- Log file: \`Documents\NinjaTrader 8\logs\BracketPRO_Debug.log\`

**Important**: Always click **Save** to persist your settings!

