## Common Questions

**Q: Nothing happens when I drag?**
- âœ“ Is button GREEN (ON)?
- âœ“ Do you have an active position?
- âœ“ Are you dragging in the price area (not indicator panel)?

**Q: How do I change the R:R ratio?**
- Press **Ctrl+Shift+R** to cycle, or click **âš™** â†’ Risk/Reward tab

**Q: Can I customize the R:R ratios?**
- Yes! Click **âš™** â†’ Risk/Reward tab â†’ Select "Custom" â†’ Enter your values

**Q: How do I enable position scaling?**
- Click **âš™** â†’ Bracket Sets tab â†’ Check "Enable Multiple Bracket Sets"

**Q: Where's the overlay?**
- Make sure it's enabled: **âš™** â†’ Display tab â†’ Check "Show Drag Overlay"
- Try different positions (Top Right, Top Left, Follow Mouse)

**Q: Can I change hotkeys?**
- Not currently - hotkeys are fixed to Ctrl+Shift+B and Ctrl+Shift+R

**Q: Does PRO require a license?**
- Yes, PRO requires a user-based license (Vendor ID: 492) tied to your NinjaTrader account.

**Q: Can I customize the breakeven button tick values?**
- Yes! Click **âš™** â†’ Position Management tab â†’ Configure BE Button 1 and BE Button 2 tick values (any positive integer)

**Q: Can I change the trailing stop tick amount?**
- Yes! Click **âš™** â†’ Position Management tab â†’ Set trailing stop ticks (common values: 5, 10, 15, 20, or custom)

**Q: Can I disable the breakeven or trailing stop buttons?**
- Yes! Click **âš™** â†’ Position Management tab â†’ Uncheck "Enable" for any button you don't want to see

**Q: Do the position management features work on Sim accounts?**
- Yes! All features (breakeven, trailing stop) work on both Sim and Live accounts.

