## Troubleshooting

### "Nothing happens when I drag"
- âœ“ Is the tool ON? (button shows green)
- âœ“ Do you have an active position?
- âœ“ Are you dragging in the price area (not indicator panel)?

### "Orders didn't place"
- âœ“ Check you have an account selected in Chart Trader
- âœ“ Verify drag direction matches position type
- âœ“ Enable debug logging: **âš™** â†’ Advanced â†’ Check "Enable Debug Logging"
- âœ“ Check log file: \`Documents\NinjaTrader 8\logs\BracketPRO_Debug.log\`

### "Overlay not showing"
- âœ“ Go to Settings â†’ Display â†’ Check "Show Drag Overlay"
- âœ“ Try different overlay positions (Top Right, Top Left, Follow Mouse)
- âœ“ Make sure you're actively dragging (not just hovering)

### "Settings don't save"
- âœ“ Click the **Save** button (not Cancel or X)
- âœ“ Restart NinjaTrader to ensure persistence

### "Hotkeys not working"
- âœ“ Make sure Chart Trader is open (Ctrl+T)
- âœ“ Click on the chart to give it focus
- âœ“ Restart NinjaTrader if needed

### "Breakeven buttons not working"
- âœ“ Make sure you have active position
- âœ“ Verify you have stop orders placed
- âœ“ Check debug log for errors
- âœ“ Ensure buttons are enabled in settings

### "Trailing stop not following price"
- âœ“ Verify button shows green (active state)
- âœ“ Check price is actually moving in favorable direction
- âœ“ Trailing stop only moves when price reaches new high/low
- âœ“ Enable debug logging to see trailing stop updates

### "Wrong prices calculated"
- âœ“ Check your current R:R ratio (shown on button)
- âœ“ Press Ctrl+Shift+R if you want different ratio
- âœ“ Watch overlay to confirm calculations before releasing
- âœ“ Verify entry price in Chart Trader matches expectation

